https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gkd0n/	5812
<p itemprop="description">国庆长假结束了，大家过节是胖三斤贴秋膘？还是坚持多运动？</p><p itemprop="description">在刚结束的伦敦马拉松精英赛上，除了基普乔格跌出前三之外，另一新闻就是KIPCHUMBA Vincent差一点点就帮<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/729/" data-brandid="729" target="_blank">adidas</a>“扬眉吐气”了。</p><p itemprop="description">今天我就来晒双adidas<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/paobuxie/" target="_blank">跑鞋</a>。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gkd0n/pic_2/' target='_blank'><img alt="配色骚+传统薄底，adidas adizero adios 5竞速跑鞋" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202009/30/5f741c6b041d23245.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">这双鞋是adios 5。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gkd0n/pic_3/' target='_blank'><img alt="配色骚+传统薄底，adidas adizero adios 5竞速跑鞋" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/30/5f741c6b845ca7373.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">这双是传统薄底跑鞋。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gkd0n/pic_4/' target='_blank'><img alt="配色骚+传统薄底，adidas adizero adios 5竞速跑鞋" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202009/30/5f741c726bf3c5445.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">厚底的Adidas adizero adios Pro我当然想要，但是买不起啊！</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gkd0n/pic_5/' target='_blank'><img alt="配色骚+传统薄底，adidas adizero adios 5竞速跑鞋" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/30/5f741c74339f32566.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">这年头，都搞厚底鞋，还坚持薄底的品牌不多了。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gkd0n/pic_6/' target='_blank'><img alt="配色骚+传统薄底，adidas adizero adios 5竞速跑鞋" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202009/30/5f741c7c0c00f8219.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">科技方面，还是老样子boost，不过这次还多了一层lightstrike包裹，也算双重科技了。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/az5gkd0n/pic_7/' target='_blank'><img alt="配色骚+传统薄底，adidas adizero adios 5竞速跑鞋" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/30/